<item>
            <title>[CONFIGURATION-387] interpolate include file names</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CONFIGURATION-387</link>
                <project id="12310467" key="CONFIGURATION">Commons Configuration</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;currently file names are not interpolated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;thus&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;inlude=$&lt;/p&gt;
{os.name}
&lt;p&gt;.$&lt;/p&gt;
{os.arch}
&lt;p&gt;.libs.conf&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;throws an exception.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;adding fileName = interpolate(fileName);&lt;br/&gt;
to PropertiesConfiguration.loadIncludeFile()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;resolves the issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
